<p>Ten days is the sweet spot for a Tanzania safari — long enough to see the full Northern Circuit at a relaxed pace, with time to photograph properly, wait for the perfect lion hunt, and not feel rushed between parks. This complete 10-day Tanzania safari itinerary covers Tarangire, three nights in the Serengeti, the Ngorongoro Crater, an Arusha cultural tour, and the lower slopes of Kilimanjaro. Here is exactly what to do, day by day, with costs, logistics, and insider tips from our Arusha-based guide team.</p>

