<h2>What to Pack for 10 Days in Tanzania</h2>
<p>Key packing essentials for a 10-day safari: neutral-coloured clothing (khaki, olive, beige — not white or bright colours), lightweight layers for cool Ngorongoro mornings (it can be 8–12°C at the crater rim), a fleece or light down jacket, good walking shoes for cultural days, high-SPF sunscreen (the equatorial sun is intense), DEET insect repellent, binoculars (minimum 8×42), a camera with 200mm+ zoom lens, a wide-brim hat, and a small daypack.</p>
<p>See our complete <a href="/tanzania-safari-packing-list-2026">Tanzania safari packing list</a> for a printable checklist.</p>

